N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 1 ยง 150.6 - Compliance with other regulations

State Regulations

Compliance with the regulations in this Part shall not
relieve failure to comply with any additional applicable international, federal, state, county, regional or local law or regulation. Notes
